        "rta_title": "",
        "rta_text1": "<p>The Grand Soleil Vintage Cup returns in 2026, scheduled for June 13–14.<br/>An unmissable event that blends competitive spirit with the pleasure of sailing, dedicated to owners of Grand Soleil achts manufactured before 2000, with the following models added this year:</p><p><br/>• Grand Soleil 40 Paperini/Duck Design<br/>• Grand Soleil 45 J&V<br/>• Grand Soleil 50 J&V<br/>• Grand Soleil 56 Briand<br/><br/>More than just a regatta, the Grand Soleil Vintage Cup is a tribute to the yachts that have shaped the brand’s history, celebrating their timeless design and technical excellence. A unique opportunity to share a passion for the sea and experience the Grand Soleil legacy firsthand.<br/><br/>Once again, the event will take place in the stunning setting of Portopiccolo, overlooking the Adriatic Sea, where sport and conviviality come together. Alongside the racing, the program will feature exclusive social moments, including a cocktail gathering and the final prize-giving ceremony.<br/><br/><strong>For more information: info@dnsistiana.it | squaggiotti@cantieredelpardo.com</strong></p>",
